---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Lönelotsarna – Experts in wage formation and salary and pay equity reviews"
  description="We provide support in matters related to wage formation, job evaluation, and pay equity reviews. We also provide Lonelots - a user-friendly and cost free tool for job evaluation and pay survey."
>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <img src={`${base}/images/Lönelotsarna.jpg`} alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/30"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center text-white">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-medium uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">
        Experts in wage formation and salary and pay equity reviews
      </h1>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto text-white/90 mb-4">
        Welcome to Lönelotsarna! We provide support in matters related to wage formation,
        job evaluation, and pay equity reviews.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto text-white/90 mb-8">
        We also provide Lonelots — a user-friendly and cost free tool for job evaluation and pay survey.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:info@lonelotsarna.se"
        class="inline-block bg-white text-brand-text font-medium px-8 py-3 uppercase tracking-wider text-sm hover:bg-brand-gray transition-colors">
        Contact us
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Services -->
  <section id="about" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-12 text-center">Our services</h2>

      <!-- The Lonelots Tool -->
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">The Lonelots Tool</h3>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
          The Lonelots tool is a weighted multi-factor and gender-neutral job evaluation tool
          that you can download free of charge. The system is based on the main areas of the
          Swedish Discrimination Act — knowledge and skills, responsibility, effort, and working
          conditions, factors that are globally recognized as essential for defining equivalent work.
          The system is a basic model with factors, aspects, and levels designed so that each user
          can adapt the method to their operations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
          The tool consists of two parts: a job evaluation system to assess which work is equivalent
          and a pay audit tool that provides the tables and charts needed to map and analyse wages
          in equal and equivalent work.
        </p>
        <a href={`${base}/en/analys-lonelots`}
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-red font-medium hover:text-brand-red-dark transition-colors">
          Download and get started
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13.5 4.5L21 12m0 0l-7.5 7.5M21 12H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Consultancy Services -->
      <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Consultancy services</h3>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-brand-text mb-2">Consultancy support</h4>
            <p class="text-brand-text/70">
              The Lonelots consultants can support you with parts of or with the full pay survey process,
              from start to end. Based on your needs we will offer a support model that is qualitative and efficient.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-brand-text mb-2">Trainings</h4>
            <p class="text-brand-text/70">
              Do you need to skill up in the area of salary reviews? We deliver open trainings in Swedish
              as well as customised trainings based on your needs (also available in English).
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="font-medium text-brand-text mb-2">Salary setting — process and structure</h4>
            <p class="text-brand-text/70">
              Lönelotsarna can help you develop salary policy and guidelines, an annual cycle for the
              salary process, individual salary setting criteria and documentation templates for
              employee and salary conversations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-brand-text/70 mt-6">
          Would you like to know more about how we can support you?
          <a href="mailto:info@lonelotsarna.se" class="text-brand-red hover:text-brand-red-dark">Contact us</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Job Evaluation and Pay Review -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-brand-gray">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-12 text-center">Job evaluation and pay review</h2>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Job evaluation</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
            To manage your job evaluation in the Lonelots tool, after downloading the program,
            follow the seven steps described in the Job Evaluation Guideline.
          </p>
          <a href={`${base}/documents/Lonelots+Job+Evaluation+Guideline+2025.pdf`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-red font-medium hover:text-brand-red-dark transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" /></svg>
            Job Evaluation Guideline (PDF)
          </a>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Pay review</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
            After you have carried out the job evaluation, you are ready for the pay review.
            Follow the seven steps described in our Pay Survey Guideline to conduct a pay survey
            and analyse the results.
          </p>
          <a href={`${base}/documents/Pay+Survey+Guideline+2025.pdf`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-brand-red font-medium hover:text-brand-red-dark transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" /></svg>
            Pay Survey Guideline (PDF)
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mt-8">
        If you have questions or need support, contact us at
        <a href="mailto:info@lonelotsarna.se" class="text-brand-red hover:text-brand-red-dark">info@lonelotsarna.se</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Structural Wage Gap -->
  <section id="reports" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 text-center">The Structural Wage Gap</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-4">
        Structural wage differences refer to wage disparities between groups of women and men
        that cannot be explained by differences in job requirements, the complexity of the work,
        or the employees' performance and skills. Instead, these pay gaps may stem from value
        discrimination, meaning that certain occupations and tasks are considered less valuable
        or important, often those traditionally performed unpaid by women.
      </p>
      <p class="text-brand-text/70 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        We publish annual reports on the structural wage gap in Sweden. We do so by comparing
        occupations across sectors and assessing them using the Lonelots job evaluation tool.
      </p>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <a href={`${base}/documents/Highly+valued+-+low+pay.pdf`} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="block bg-brand-gray p-6 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow group">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-brand-text group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors">Highly valued — low pay</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-brand-text/60 mt-1">Our report on the structural wage gap between female-dominated and other occupations.</p>
            </div>
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-brand-text/30 group-hover:text-brand-red transition-colors shrink-0" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About Us -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-brand-gray">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-8 text-center">About us</h2>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
          The Lönelotsarna team is a group of consultants with extensive experience, specialised
          in wage formation, salary review and equal pay.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
          We are also a non-profit organisation working for equal pay by developing methods,
          raising awareness and driving the public debate on equal pay. We have developed the
          Lonelots tool for job evaluation and provide it free of charge. We also publish
          annual reports on the structural pay gap.
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-text/70">
          Read more about us in the newsletter Les Glorieuses:
          <em>"Meet the Equal Pay Super Geeks who proved that midwives deserve the same pay as engineers"</em>,
          published October 2024 — in
          <a href="https://thegloriousletter.com/equal-pay-super-geeks/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-red hover:text-brand-red-dark">English</a>
          and
          <a href="https://lesglorieuses.fr/les-super-geeks/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-brand-red hover:text-brand-red-dark">French</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium text-brand-text uppercase tracking-wider mb-6">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-4">
        Want to know more about how we can support you, attend a demo or have other questions?
      </p>
      <p class="text-brand-text/70 mb-2">
        Once a month we have an open demo of the Lonelots tool in Swedish.
        If you are not a Swedish speaker, contact us for a demo in English.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-6">
        <a href="mailto:info@lonelotsarna.se" class="text-brand-red font-medium hover:text-brand-red-dark text-lg">info@lonelotsarna.se</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>
